AngularJS 依赖注入$inject程序会自动加载依赖，不需要写代码

控制器格式：
1、myApp.controller('DoubleCtrl', ['$scope', function($scope) {
    $scope.double = function(value) { return value * 2; };
}]);

2、app.controller('myCtrl', function($scope) {
   $scope.firstName = "John";
   $scope.lastName = "Doe";
});
